{"tid":1900553,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"連登仔害撚死人，今日去食撈麵比個樓面打到仆街","createTime":"2020-02-27T09:42:30.000Z","updateTime":"2020-02-27T09:53:23.000Z","uid":64131,"like":3,"dislike":7,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"e5540c9fe7fee73fa46c0bc89991f050dce4f975","tid":1900553,"uid":64131,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-27T09:42:30.000Z","msg":"又話乜鳩廣東人傳統<br />\n食撈麵要「一乾三濕」<br />\n即係麵、湯、茶、汁 四樣<br />\n無論食雲吞麵 雲吞撈麵 都一定要上齊呢四樣<br />\n如果食撈麵 最正宗最傳統o既食法應該係先飲茶漱口<br />\n之後加醬油落兜湯度 食幾啖麵 含一啖湯<br />\n一野噴落個小二身上<br />\n「屌! 咁難食點食呀! 」<br />\n我咪照做囉<br />\n點知比個MK樓面兜個糖罐車落我個頭度<br />\n屌哂老母話我播毒<br />\n連登仔真係害撚死人"},{"pid":"3992a0f66bc2ab47044472e5014eb97697a245c8","tid":1900553,"uid":241504,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-27T09:44:23.000Z","msg":"開乜膠？pull"},{"pid":"fa0a19ca321b5d6ea4595b4f42b5ae22829bd55c","tid":1900553,"uid":115655,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-27T09:44:53.000Z","msg":"樓主好cute"},{"pid":"98e71f71ea485d0d50787a8f8e503cd38d1467eb","tid":1900553,"uid":242537,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-27T09:45:02.000Z","msg":"開體育台做乜膠野<br />\n拉<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6e6aadd5750e729d5a76a4beff689744529813df","tid":1900553,"uid":256952,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-27T09:46:34.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/3rC0LYu.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F3rC0LYu.gif&h=e0233cdb&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"3e7d9a67a6686d14c8cdd636cc236608be16cbb6","tid":1900553,"uid":196924,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-27T09:51:05.000Z","msg":"陳淨心唔係人形便器咩"},{"pid":"14057ca500e82f56bc952a33d0